snippet.title: Identifile | Early Gameplay Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist on Steam now!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3054210/Identifile/

Identifile is a file explorer roguelike dungeon crawler - Play as the cursor and fend off viruses by circling them! Acquire modifiers and EXE files that change the game up, keeping each run unique. Will you uncover what truly lurks within your computer?
